	'docs/tables/'.
	* Added code to create the 'TTYS' table in 'rd_create_db'.
	* Added a 'RDTty' class in 'lib/'.
	* Added code to create the 'DECKS' table in 'rd_create_db'.
	* Added a 'RDDeck' class in 'lib/'.
