	* Fixed a bug in 'rdcatch/edit_upload.cpp' that was allowing URLs
	utilizing the http and https protocols to be entered.
	* Implemented Upload Events in RDCatch for the smb: and ftp:
	protocols.
2005-08-03 Fred Gleason <fredg@salemradiolabs.com>
	* Added 'RDRecording::Interrupted', 'RDRecording::RecordActive',
	'RDRecording::Waiting, and 'RDRecording::PlayActive' values to the
	'RDRecording::ExitCode' enum in 'lib/rdrecording.h'.
	* Added code to 'rdcatchd/rdcatchd.cpp' to flag interrupted events
	in the database.
	* Added code to 'rdcatchd/rdcatchd.cpp' to properly notify new
	instances of RDCatch about currently active xload events.
	* Fixed a bug in 'rdcatchd/rdcatchd.cpp' that was causing causing
	attempts to abort playout events to fail.
	* Added exit code support for Record and Playout events in
	RDCatch.
