2005-10-17 Fred Gleason <fredg@salemradiolabs.com>
	* Added a 'LOGS.IMPORT_DATE' field to the database.
	* Added 'FADEUP_POINT', 'FADEUP_GAIN', 'FADEDOWN_POINT',
	'FADEDOWN_GAIN' and 'SEGUE_GAIN' fields to the log table format in
	the database.
	* Incremented the database version to 93.
