	* Increased MAX_GPIO_PINS to 192 in 'lib/rd.h'.
2006-06-21 Fred Gleason <fredg@salemradiolabs.com>
	* Added 'SERVICES.MUS_BREAK_STRING' and
	'SERVICES.MUS_TRACK_STRING' fields to the database.
	* Changed the default value of 'VGUEST_RESOURCES.SURFACE_NUM' to
	'0' in the database.
	* Incremented the database version to 113.
	* Fixed a bug in 'lib/rdsvc.cpp' that was causing importing logs
	for services whose name contained '-' characters to fail.
	* Added 'Insert Traffic Break String' and 'Insert Voice Track
	String' controls in 'rdadmin/edit_svc.cpp'.
	* Added code in 'lib/rdsvc.cpp' and 'lib/rdlog_event.cpp' to
	generate embedded track markers from music log imports.
