	to voice_tracker.cpp
	* Fixed waveform display and scrolling for custom start and end points
	in voice_tracker.cpp
	* Added duck gain support during playback in voice_tracker.cpp
	* Added duck gain support during recording in voice_tracker.cpp
	* Added code to set the duck volumes with the rubber band in
	voice_tracker.cpp
	* Added code to show the fade and duck volume using the meter in
	voice_tracker.cpp
	* Added auto segue during recording (like in rdairplay) to
	voice_tracker.cpp
	* Changed the behavior of "Do Over" for better handling of custom
	start and end points
	* Changed TRACKER_MB_PER_PIXEL to 42 in voice_tracker.h
	* Changed TRACKER_MIN_GAIN to -3000 in voice_tracker.h
	* Set TRACKER_FORCED_SEGUE to 1000 ms in voice_tracker.h
