2007-07-15 Stefan Gabriel <stg@st-gabriel.de>
	* Added code to lib/rd_button_panel.cpp to enable CopyTo, AddTo and
	DeleteTo Sound Panel Buttons with the COPY, ADD and DELTE buttons
	* Added code to lib/rdsound_panel.cpp to enable CopyTo, AddTo and
	DeleteTo Sound Panel Buttons with the COPY, ADD and DELTE buttons
        * Changed RDBaseSearchText() (lib/rdcart_search_text.cpp) to implement
	AND (by space) logic when filterinG carts. Use quotes to search for
	exact phrase
