	* Fixed a bug in 'rdlogmanager/edit_eventline.cpp' where adding an
	event by means of typing in a name without exactly matching the
	case of the event name would result in a corrupt clock record
	[Mantis #229].
2007-11-13 Fred Gleason <fredg@paravelsystems.com>
	* Changed the behavior of the 'LL' ['Load Log'] RML so that
	passing a '-2' for the start line argument will start the log at
	the start only if the transition type of the first log event is
	not 'stop'.
	* Fixed a bug in 'rdairplay/log_play.cpp' that was causing a
	chained-to log to start even if its initial event had s Stop
	transition.
