2008-07-18 Stefan Gabriel <stg@st-gabriel.de>
 	* Moved code to create *_STACK tables brach to
	'rdlogmanager/generate_log.cpp'.
 	Note: Stack Tables are not linked to Logs, but to Services; they
	are the schedulers history of selected carts.
