 	cae/cae_hpi.cpp, cae/cae_alsa.cpp, cae/cae_jack.cpp and
 	lib/rdedit_audio.cpp
 	* Fixed a bug in lib/rdsimpleplayer.cpp; simpleplayer played on
	more then one port under some conditions
 	* Fixed a bug in rdlogedit/voice_tracker.cpp: added missing
	destructors for wavepainters wpg[i]
 	* Fixed a bug in rdlibrary/edit_cart.cpp that caused a segfault
	when editing more than one cart.
