	name that contained spaces.
2008-10-24 Fred Gleason <fredg@paravelsystems.com>
	* Fixed a bug in 'rdlogmanager/add_clock.cpp' that caused a
	segfault when creating a clock with a name longer than 58
	characters.
	* Fixed a bug in 'rdlogmanager/add_event.cpp' that caused a
	segfault when creating an event with a name longer than 58
	characters.
