	* Added 'STATIONS.CUE_CARD', 'STATIONS.CUE_PORT',
	'STATIONS.CARTSLOT_COLUMNS' and 'STATIONS.CARTSLOT_ROWS'
	fields to the database.
	* Incremented the database version to 213.
