2018-03-11 Fred Gleason <fredg@paravelsystems.com>
	* Converted ripcd(8) to use RDApplication.
	* Documented a 'Notification' message type in
	'docs/apis/notification.xml'.
	* Added an 'RDMulticaster' class.
